Introduction to Power BI
-What is Power BI
It is a business analytics tools developed by Microsoft that enables user to visualize and analyze data with greater speed ,efficiency and understanding 

-Compenent of Power BI
Power BI Desktop
Power BI Services
Power BI Mobile Apps
Power BI Report servers

-Key features of Power BI
Data Connectactivity 
Data Transformation 
visulization
DAX(Data Analysis Expression)

-Benefits of using Power BI
Ease to use
Real-Time Insight
Collabrating and sharing
Cost -Effective
Integration with other tools

--Who can Benefit from Power BI
Business analysts ,data analysts,and data scientist
Decision-makers and executive 
IT professions
